为了保证您的银泰礼品卡资金安全，请设置支付密码

<%= form_tag(ims_accounts_path, :method => 'post') do %>
<%= hidden_field_tag "sms_code", params[:sms_code]%>
<%= password_field_tag "pwd", "" %><br />
<%= password_field_tag "comfirm_pwd", "" %><br />
<%= submit_tag "确认", id: "submit" %>

<% end %>

支付密码可以用于礼品卡查询和购买支付，请妥善保管

<%= content_for :javascripts do %>
<script>
  $(document).ready(function() {
    $("#submit").click(function(){
      if($("#pwd").val() != $("#comfirm_pwd").val()){
        alert("请输入一致的密码");
        return false;
      }
    });
  });
</script>
<% end %>